summary: Alexis Rodriguez is a 30-year-old Financial Analyst based in Los Angeles, originally from New York. She identifies as a straight female using she/her/hers pronouns. Alexis graduated from New York University and works in the finance industry. She values family, hard work, and curiosity, and enjoys traveling, learning new languages, and the culinary arts. Religion is important to her as a Catholic, and she leans more on the liberal side politically. She is seeking a life partner and is open to having children in the future. Alexis owns a cat, doesn't use drugs, but enjoys a drink occasionally. Her partner preferences are a straight man between the ages of 28 and 35 who does not smoke or use drugs. He should also be active and open to having children.
